channel.title: How to take this item off the wall? 317 delta!
channel.description:
[url=http://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/812/evolved0001.png/]http://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/812/evolved0001.png/[/url]
I cannot manage to take this off the wall... I went into client.java and put: makeGlobalObject(3209, 3217, 6951, -2, 10);
6951 = nothing and it works for all my walls.... im not sure please help?? I have the right coords i know i do, please tell me what else I need to do?
Thanks!

item.title: How to take this item off the wall? 317 delta!
item.dc:creator: @mista_pnut mista pnut
item.description:
@mista_pnut wrote:

Maybe it’s just positioned on a different height level. I’ve edited my deleteObject void so that it can handle heights for such things. You’ll have to do the same and delete the object via coordinates and heightLevel.
